Package: OfflineGeocodingTool
Title: Offline Geocoding Using Statistics Canada ODA
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Geocode Canadian addresses offline using the Open Database of
    Addresses (ODA) with exact and fuzzy matching, composite scoring
    (text similarity, numeric nearness, geographic proximity), and optional
    manual review of fuzzy matches.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    stringdist,
    fuzzyjoin,
    rlang
Suggests:
    testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
